text.tspan: Every dish we sampled was delicious, a highlight being the hainan chicken rice, but there was
so much more that I would never have tried if it weren't for going with an experienced guide.
She even brought us to the beach view where we tried the famous Singapore crab dish...
The price was a little expensive, but that is my only complaint. We got to explore places we
didn’t even imagine we will because they are so “hidden” even from the reviews online. For
example, the bar near the concierge at a hotel! *** WAI KIT
